{"id": 2775, "genre": 1001, "title": "你的爸妈在社交网络上有多努力？", "description": "你妈，一位天道酬勤的网上邻居。（题图来自：iStock ©️Krimzoya）", "record_count": 1711, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190131154456kcVErjzmonKu6JyG.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-02-09T17:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 326917, "content": "微信发一些鸡汤视频", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1579149}, {"id": 327175, "content": "我发了带英文的朋友圈，她会自己偷偷查中文", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1514209}, {"id": 326925, "content": "我妈，迷上了拼多多，微信支付，支付宝支付全都挡不住她。今年大家庭聚会有叔叔姑埋怨现在电子产品难用，用不懂，我妈妈义正言辞的说那是你们跟不上时代了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 335185}, {"id": 327186, "content": "有N个姐妹群聊！每天查看我的朋友圈！各种点赞！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1497481}, {"id": 327192, "content": "爸你可以多用一些表情....\n然后...你好\u0014/微笑\u0014/ \n           再见/微笑+手掌/", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1449733}, {"id": 329760, "content": "貌似我是个意外", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1595636}, {"id": 327222, "content": "想他们", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1582466}, {"id": 338498, "content": "。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1605759}, {"id": 326724, "content": "会在做好炫拍后问你好看不", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1579133}, {"id": 330565, "content": "妈觉得拼多多挺好用的 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1491729}, {"id": 326725, "content": "致力于分享各种觉得有用链接，内容从做人哲学到用电安全", "image": "img/option/option/2019021001170019fN6TMhuRr3gtow", "praise_count": 295, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 156328}, {"id": 326726, "content": "爷爷奶奶经常问我各种网络用语的意思，比如呵呵，微笑脸的真正含义，表情包等等", "image": null, "praise_count": 31, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1480187}, {"id": 326727, "content": "抢红包，还非要叫我，我死了", "image": null, "praise_count": 152, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1531372}, {"id": 326728, "content": "怎么教都学不会淘宝和刷交通卡，然而一个学期回来我妈妈拼多多玩的贼6😣。还认真询问我“挖槽”是什么。", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 78499}, {"id": 326729, "content": "过年都没人来评论了…", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1440612}, {"id": 326731, "content": "我妈简直不能太666，退休以后支付宝理财，微信付款，三大视频网站VIP（最近在看腾讯的父母爱情），还能用苹果手机定位功能判断我是不是偷懒没有去上班。", "image": null, "praise_count": 52, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1461746}, {"id": 326732, "content": "支付宝各种农场活动 抢红包 几乎所有里面的活动都乐此不疲的参加", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1578837}, {"id": 326733, "content": "婚礼后看随份子的名单有很多网名，类似白云、黑土啥的，才知道我爸的网友来了两桌。他是几个QQ群的管理员，同时担任群出游的摄影师，基本差不多每周都会参加群集体出游，游山玩水的。我挺开心，他退休后在这个网络时代也找到了一群朋友。", "image": null, "praise_count": 203, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1466525}, {"id": 326734, "content": "每天手机突然卡了的时候，就是我妈打视频进来的时候。", "image": null, "praise_count": 55, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1519342}, {"id": 326736, "content": "突然收到一个小程序 快来看看我重返十八岁的样子", "image": null, "praise_count": 29, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1578980}, {"id": 326737, "content": "学拼音", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1568030}, {"id": 326994, "content": "妈妈对于拼多多的操作了如指掌", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1489345}, {"id": 326739, "content": "我需要廣大群眾的關愛眼神😍\n別著急走，點個讚唄🤘", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1565805}, {"id": 326741, "content": "非常喜欢用微信视频联系你，并且不会提前问你方便与否，就这样来了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 82, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1192836}, {"id": 326742, "content": "让我熟悉了一个应用叫美篇", "image": null, "praise_count": 85, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1554183}, {"id": 326747, "content": "抖音已经玩的出神入化。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1579341}, {"id": 327006, "content": "今天给我妈妈的探探卸了装了Soul\n我是魔鬼", "image": "img/option/option/20190211225651RpAZiPrsMKbv7CDW", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1192633}, {"id": 326751, "content": "拉了个家族群，晚辈都不在里面，还天天告诉你他们在群里说什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1579380}, {"id": 326752, "content": "定时在支付宝收取我的绿色能量，之后还在微信里告诉我要少花点钱😂", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1579385}, {"id": 327009, "content": "加了好多微信群 觉得太吵了 又设置成消息免打扰", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1490785}, {"id": 326754, "content": "通过朋友圈背景了解你的恋爱状况🤷🏻‍♀️🤷🏻‍♀️🤷🏻‍♀️", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1512337}, {"id": 326755, "content": "各种转发", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1526235}, {"id": 326757, "content": "比我想象的要努力", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1573739}, {"id": 326759, "content": "学会了刷抖音！", "image": null, "praise_count": 50, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1579387}, {"id": 326760, "content": "你们这算啥，我外公说他电脑太卡了，叫我买个内存条", "image": null, "praise_count": 66, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1508794}, {"id": 326765, "content": "热衷于社交网络平台，微信，朋友圈，美篇，抖音，广场舞等软件应用自如。因为她们需要放飞心灵，实现自我。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1579485}, {"id": 326767, "content": "不努力", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1513949}, {"id": 326768, "content": "就止家族群里聊，界面字特大，声音放最大", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1561243}, {"id": 326769, "content": "天天看我微信步数来判断我一天到底出没出门、是在宿舍睡一天还是去图书馆学习了，搞得跟神探一样", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1487000}, {"id": 328050, "content": "啊", "image": "img/option/option/20190218130422QtYWnK8bGcD6I1E3.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1586869}, {"id": 326771, "content": "我妈因为无法登陆视频客户端急了，视频一看，她居然注册了一个新的。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1579525}, {"id": 326773, "content": "我和我妈的微信记录，算是养生文", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1247974}, {"id": 326776, "content": "微信小程序关注了糖豆广场舞，每天都看🙄", "image": "img/option/option/20190210155131xj4XSL9tnEBvgrAC", "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1110422}, {"id": 326777, "content": "在家微信每天一教，教完就忘，问多了我烦了声音一大就说我吼他", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1577758}, {"id": 326779, "content": "哔哩哔哩\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1573434}, {"id": 327035, "content": "流连于各个微信群努力保持回复与发信息，是我爸退休后每天最努力的工作。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1578405}, {"id": 326780, "content": "？？？\n/", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1569336}, {"id": 326781, "content": "？？？！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1569336}, {"id": 326783, "content": "所有抢红包送流量的活动一概参加，并转发抄送三个家庭群...", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 958754}, {"id": 326786, "content": "打电话不接\n用微信打过来", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 770585}]}